WEBVTT

00:07:57.967 --> 00:08:00.890
nastavili da vodite vrlo
nezavisne živote.

00:08:00.890 --> 00:08:03.211
Zapravo, niste čak ni živeli zajedno.

00:08:03.211 --> 00:08:05.045
MK: Mi smo imali "brak na daljinu"

00:08:05.045 --> 00:08:08.100
U našem slučaju 
u pitanju je bio Vašington,

00:08:08.100 --> 00:08:09.223
Hjuston, Tuson.

00:08:09.223 --> 00:08:10.903
Nekada bismo putovali u pravcu


00:08:10.903 --> 00:08:12.457
kazaljke na satu, nekada obrnuto

00:08:12.457 --> 00:08:14.072
u sva ta mesta,

00:08:14.072 --> 00:08:17.949
i nismo zaista zajedno živeli

00:08:17.949 --> 00:08:20.249
sve do tog subotnjeg jutra.

00:08:20.249 --> 00:08:22.547
U roku od sat vremena,
nakon Gebinog ranjavanja

00:08:22.547 --> 00:08:24.439
ja sam bio u avionu na putu ka Tusonu,

00:08:24.439 --> 00:08:26.010
i to je bio momenat

00:08:26.010 --> 00:08:28.753
u kojem se to promenilo.

00:08:28.753 --> 00:08:31.245
PM: Gebi, vi ste se
kandidovali za Kongres